{"tid":2092781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"洪水平穩通過三峽 暴雨預警解除","createTime":"2020-07-03T11:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T08:35:23.000Z","uid":225931,"like":13,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"97503ff84f2091a63817b8fc6a26e5238bb4c04b","tid":2092781,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/743d45390d35e5e9ac912335914f48ab.jpg/WP7KRNyhHHu-6FL_DISxsjfs0CJ0uU0tLmFbrS5hW60?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F743d45390d35e5e9ac912335914f48ab.jpg%2FWP7KRNyhHHu-6FL_DISxsjfs0CJ0uU0tLmFbrS5hW60%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=34ba0ebe&s={SIZE}\" />截至周四（2日）下午2時，今年長江1號洪水平穩通過三峽庫區，洪峰流量達到每秒5.3萬立方米，三峽水庫控制下泄流量每秒3.5萬立方米，有效攔蓄削減洪峰，削峰率達到34%，減輕中下游防洪壓力。<br />\n<br />\n中央氣象台周五上午6時<span style=\"color: red;\">解除暴雨藍色預警</span>，意味連續31天的暴雨預警暫時解除。預計周五白天到夜間，南方地區雨勢將短暫減弱，但安徽南部、浙江中北部、江西中北部、湖南中北部、雲南中西部、西藏東南部等地仍有較強降雨，江西中北部、浙江中部等局地暴雨或大暴雨。從周六起，西南地區至長江中下游一帶的降雨將再度增強。"},{"pid":"d301121e03ee5cfaca6bfa25344f3d297ab8697e","tid":2092781,"uid":155095,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"連登燈完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6db4dbaad7a474e490226458314fb1a6fa555c","tid":2092781,"uid":292497,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都頂到"},{"pid":"5fc96067ec8d0bf4926890db8fa474d1d8625d8d","tid":2092781,"uid":216828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"無事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056c069f421a6bc9eebc758cb030d221a9aa419d","tid":2092781,"uid":359022,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"工程師話 過度張弛 收唔返 好似係<im